snippet.title: Eggcelerate! Coming to Steam March 30th
snippet.description:
Carry an egg through loops and over jumps with your racecar, being careful not to drop it! Laugh, cry, scream and shout with hilarious failures and amazing victories. Don't crack up!

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1535490/Eggcelerate/
Daily Live Streams: https://www.twitch.tv/timbeaudet
Discord Community: https://www.tyrebyt.es/discord
